OL,7,FOur reporter Barnaby Papadopulos sent
OL,8,Fthis report from the Dumfries and
OL,9,FGalloway Integration Joint Board
OL,10,Fmeeting on 29 October 2024. After the
OL,11,Fmeeting, he spoke with the chair of
OL,12,Fthe board, Andy McFarlane.
