OL,4,Cat Dumfries and Galloway cottage
OL,5,Chospitals
OL,7,FThe Dumfries and Galloway Integration
OL,8,FJoint Board (IJB) held a meeting to
OL,9,Fdecide the future of cottage hospitals
OL,10,Fin Moffat, Thornhill, Newton Stewart
OL,11,Fand Kirkcudbright, on 29 October 2024.
OL,13,FThe decision involved considerations
OL,14,Franging from reinstating in-patient
OL,15,Fcare to shutting down the hospitals
OL,16,Fand selling off the land.
OL,18,FThis year a consultation was held to
OL,19,Fallow the public to offer their views
OL,20,Fon the future of the sites, which have
OL,21,Fbeen closed to in-patients since 2020.
