OL,7,FWhich options were considered?
OL,9,FAt a meeting earlier this month,
OL,10,FDumfries and Galloway Council rejected
OL,11,Fall six options, instead recommending
OL,12,Fa 'blended' option that would have
OL,13,Fseen outpatient services combined with
OL,14,Fsome bed-based services.
OL,16,FHowever, IJB board members disagreed,
OL,17,Fdeciding on option three, which will
OL,18,Fsee no return to in-patient services,
OL,19,Fan increase in community out-patient
OL,20,Fcare and day treatment and an
OL,21,Fexpansion of Home Team accommodation.
