OL,7,FIn Moffat, GP services will relocate
OL,8,Fto the cottage hospital but there will
OL,9,Fbe no return to in-patient services.
OL,11,FLast week Galloway and West Dumfries
OL,12,FScottish Conservative MSP Finlay
OL,13,FCarsons had encouraged the IJB to
OL,14,Flisten to the public's view on the
OL,15,Ffuture of their "much-loved" cottage
OL,16,Fhospitals.
