OL,7,FHe said: "The consultation process
OL,8,Fprobably attracted the biggest turn-
OL,9,Fout of the public in years and
OL,10,Fdemonstrated the strong affinity they
OL,11,Fhave with these four hospitals."
OL,13,FSpeaking after the meeting, the chair
OL,14,Fof the IJB, Andy McFarlane said: "We
OL,15,Fhave to make a decision for the whole
OL,16,Farea and I think the decision that the
OL,17,Fboard have made today is the one that
OL,18,Fis going to give us the best return
OL,19,Fand is the most deliverable.
